        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Mail sent with Zend_Mail shows up as sent to undisclosed-recipients, if Zend_Mail method addTo($email, $name) is fed with empty $name or $name equals $email.\n\nI have changed the function _formatAddress in Zend_Mail class to resolve this:\n\n{code}\nprotected function _formatAddress($email, $name)\n    {\n        if ($name && $name!='') { \n                $encodedName = $this->_encodeHeader($name);\n        } else {\n                $name = $email;\n                $encodedName = $this->_encodeHeader($email);\n        }\n        if ($encodedName === $name && strpos($name, ',') !== false) {\n              $format = '\"%s\" <%s>';\n        } else {\n                $format = '%s <%s>';\n        }\n        return sprintf($format, $encodedName, $email);\n     \n       \n    }\n{code}\n"
        },
